                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>1998-10-27</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This is a very moving collection of essays for anyone interested in how  religious thought affects the writings of authors.  I couldn't put the book  down and recommend it for discussion groups as well.</span>
                  
              
